Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:01:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The clash between Osiris and Obelisk showed us a vision of our past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba, if you insist on denying it,\N then good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But for me, without the memories\N of my past, I {\b0}have{\b1} no future!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that vision holds some truth to our fated conflict,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then I'm going to awaken it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to beat Kaiba and fulfill my promise with Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:02:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Promise Between Friends:\N The Red-Eyes Black Dragon"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's The Great War God Obelisk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} Summon\N his God Card again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!\N What the hell is Yugi doing up there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna nap for?!\N You gotta cheer him too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Support Yugi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}san{\i0}, stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to see Yugi's fight too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna let you see it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open your eyes and take a long,\N hard look, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's... Our Yugi's up there\N fighting as we speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your weakness comes from being\N trapped in your {\i1}stupid illusions{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resurrection of the Dead can only\N revive a god for one turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to the underworld, Obelisk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... It's useless to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to crush you this turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and {\i1}destroy{\i0} you along with the\N vision of the past in my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My future lies {\i1}beyond{\i0} this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My lost memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like Kaiba said, I might just be wallowing in the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I know I can't move forward until I get back what I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Despite supposedly being powerless, the Millennium Tauk showed me a vision of the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I want to make our promise into reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't let myself lose here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where the heck did everyone go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\b0}There{\b1} you are!\N Where the heck were you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:04:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I looked all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're impressive, Jounouchi!\N I can't believe you made the Best Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's cuz I've been training him well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But in all honesty, I never thought you'd make it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What'd ya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The great Katsuya Jounouchi's not satisfied with the Best Eight position!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He aims only for the championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the spirit, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your hand holds\N countless possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you keep that in mind and work hard, winning the championship may not just be a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell do\N ya mean by "may not"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You both total at 2000 Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tributing is not required.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You may only attack once per turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are not allowed to directly attack\N the player with your Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then let us begin the first match of the Quarter-Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here I go! It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will Summon Cat's Fairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must understand that Monster Cards are meant to be played in combination with Magic Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach this squirt\N the fundamentals of Dueling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I Summon Magnets #1!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then,\N the Magic Card Legendary Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Warrior-Type Monster,\N Magnets #1, has his Attack and\N Defense Power increased by 300 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I attack the Cat's Fairy\N with Magnets #1!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothin' to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It wasn't that big of a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I set one reverse card...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and then Summon\N the Lizard Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Endin' your turn\N without even {\b0}attacking{\b1}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You ain't beatin' me\N with moves like {\i0}that{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only thing a real man\N knows how to do is attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Magnets #1! Attack Lizard Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I activate my Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:07:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reinforcement!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reinforcements grants the Monster\N you attacked 500 Attack Points until the\N end of the turn it was activated in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was sent back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe you didn't even\N consider my Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must've\N made it this far by luck alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I Summon Tiger Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My turn's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're beyond reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of you lucky mortals is going\N to become my offering to the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and fill my being with the happiness\N of enjoying your hellish anguish?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and let me choose one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I grow {\i1}impatient{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you believe that our consciousnesses\N were reborn thousands of years later\N from that of a Pharaoh and a priest...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome to believe in that\N image of the past if you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you insist on believing that this Duel\N is the manifestation of a conflict that began\N 3,000 years ago, then good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then allow me to do you the favor\N of breaking that illusion\N you live by into {\i1}pieces{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0}, along with your {\i1}past{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy that past along {\i1}with{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be the {\i1}last turn{\i0}, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I switch Lord of Dragons\N into Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flute of Dragon-Summoning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flute of Dragon-Summoning...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Lord of Dragons plays this flute,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am able to Summon up to\N two Dragon-type Monsters\N in my hand to the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one set of Dragon-Types\N Kaiba would play {\i1}now{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes White Dragons!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three Blue-Eyes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's my turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll Summon Giant Steel Idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}1400 Attack Points?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's stronger than my Tiger Axe...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy's gonna be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dude, your level's way too low!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way I'd fight you\N with such low Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I activate a Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I polymerize Giant Steel Idol \Nwith Lizard Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to Summon Metal Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Metal Dragon will attack\N your Tiger Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it all! My Life...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, it's your turn now, dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't need {\b0}you{\b1} to tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Flame Swordsman?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy has 1800 Attack Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aww, damn...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's 50 Attack Points lower\N than his Metal Dragon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No helpin' it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna have to hide behind\N a Defense Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I Summon Hero of the East\N in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have four Monsters on my field.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Yugi, have nothing but\N the Black Magician and that trash Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can escape the attacks from all four Monsters this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! You lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not even Yugi can\N get out of this predicament!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My brother's got\N this Duel in the bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:13:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder which\N one of them is winning...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care which one of them wins.\N I just don't want any more casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! I'm sure\N Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0} and Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} are playing\N a fair Duel up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rooting for Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't let you get away, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Magic Card, Defense Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks to the effects\N of Defense Seal, Hero of the East\N is forced into Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Metal Dragon,\N attack Hero of the East!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aw, shit! My Life Points fell\N all the way down to 300!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I set one reverse card\N and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let me just say this, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the very definition\N of "hanging by a thread"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stuff a sock in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shield in the Right Hand,\N Sword in the Left Hand
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a card that switches\N the Attack and Defense Points\N of all Monsters on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So if I can get out a Monster that\N has higher Attack Points than his\N Metal Dragon's Defense Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aw, damn! No luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't got a Monster\N like that in my hand...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Toss in the towel already, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing you try now will\N turn the situation around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So this is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hand holds\N countless possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wind Fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's an Equipment Magic\N that increases the Attack Power\N of a Wind Monster by 400 points
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and decreases its\N Defense Power by 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hell yeah! Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I Summon the Flame Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:15:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, your Metal Dragon's a\N Wind Attribute Monster, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I'll Equip the Magic Card,\N Gust Fan, with Metal Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gust Fan is an\N Equipment Magic Card meant\N to increase your {\b0}own{\b1} Monster's Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On the contrary, purposely increasing your\N opponent's Attack Power by equipping it\N with them instead is no less than suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please be serious about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm about as serious as you can get!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm {\b0}deadly serious{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Magic Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shield in the Right Hand,\N Sword in the Left Hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With Shield in the Right Hand,\N Sword in the Left Hand in effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}both sides swap point values!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Metal Dragon's Attack Power is 1500!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Flame Swordsman has 1600!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I can't believe you\N thought of that combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now go, Flame Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Attack the Metal Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Spear 'im!\N Metal Dragon's as good as go-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Flame Swordsman was killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You see, just before you\N activated Shield in the Right Hand,\N Sword in the Left Hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I activated my Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Trap, you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Castle Walls increases Metal Dragon's\N Defense Points by 500 for\N the turn this card was activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that means it also changed with the effect of Shield in the Right Hand, Sword in the Left Hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Flame Swordsman had\N 1600 Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While Metal Dragon had 2000!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that's 400 points of damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Duel is finished!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guess I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I fought with all I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm content with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:16:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I lost completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good luck in the Semi-Finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks a lot, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not just anyone could come up\N with such a complicated combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're something else, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry for saying that\N your level was too low.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will you Duel me again some day?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sure! But I'm gonna win next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brace yourself, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And carve this\N into your memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name! The name of the {\i1}true winner{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On my field, I have Black Magician\N and Magnet Warrior Beta...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way they can stand up\N to the attacks of three Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like the endgame to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So Seto Kaiba's gonna be the first\N offering to my darkness, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Triple Attack!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this the end for me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't lose, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Didn't you always used to tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...there's always a chance, as long\N as you got cards in your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My hand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't give up, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what it means to\N be a True Duelist, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no hope left!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the light of the Burst Streams\N lead you to darkness, Yug-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}Red-Eyes{\i0}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flute of Dragon-Summoning\N lets you Special Summon Dragon-Types\N from your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that effect wasn't just\N limited to {\i1}your{\i0} hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It affected the ones in {\i1}my{\i0} hand as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Red-Eyes Black Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Soul Card\N Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still had that\N cards in your hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!\N You sure are naive, Kaiba!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then my Blue-Eyes will\N dispose of the Red-Eyes!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get rid of that pest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Triple Force\N Burst Stream of Destruction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first target is the Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse Trap, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magician's Selection!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magician's Selection?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Trap that activates only when a\N Spellcaster you control is being attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That attack is negated!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Monster with the lowest\N Attack Strength on my\N opponent's field is destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you won't be able to stop\N the {\i1}other two{\i0} attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnet Warrior Beta is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go to Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost of Jounouchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His soul can't be broken!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse Trap, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hexagram Curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster ensnared\N by the Hexagram Curse is\N rendered unable to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And their Attack Power is\N reduced by 700 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now for\N the Red-Eyes' counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Fire Bullet!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes is destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Blue-Eyes lost to\N Jounouchi's {\i1}ghost{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You gave me strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go and win, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The emergence of Red-Eyes\N interferes with my plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it won't stop me from wining!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two more Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My memories of the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My promise to a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to grasp that light,\N I will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks to the Red-Eyes Jounouchi left with him, Yugi managed to get through all three of the Blue-Eyes attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And somehow, the Summoning of Red-Eyes brought Jounouchi conscious again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi then urges us to go and cheer for Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, Yugi and Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s\N Duel reaches its climax!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.97,0:22:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Destroy the Hatred!\N Black Paladin"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.27,0:22:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.37,0:23:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.79,0:23:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.90,0:23:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.16,0:23:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
